<br />\n你知唔知太子站乘客比人打佢掹唔到；<br />\n你知唔知佢親眼睇住香港人比元朗狗打，佢唔做嘢。<br />\n你知唔知揸飛狗諗緊咩呀？<br />\n話畀你聽佢唔想做閘口揸fit人，<br />\n佢唔想入港鐵，<br />\n但係佢冇辦法，冇得返轉頭。<br />\n係呀，每個人都有偶像，我都有。<br />\n其實，讀唔讀書，我理唔到咁多，<br />\n但係我想話畀你聽，行錯路，冇得返轉頭。"},{"pid":"412927101275a684177c6f482e353a4e066d4895","tid":2422521,"uid":184992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd99237e7a56e53d87dca6093d8f36f153c0b8fe","tid":2422521,"uid":286155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"搭黨鐵<br />\n抵la"},{"pid":"6234c52198782358ab77748a0af3265c3da5d123","tid":2422521,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"喺狗鐵范圍內得到popo嘅權力， 真腐化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398ec8191825ff5d463fd60838b4a8347bdbe5f0","tid":2422521,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30787745efc38b912c5eeae5c83e8a85de704230","tid":2422521,"uid":177873,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"其實唔好咁癲啦 <br />\n<br />\n你揀得搭黨鐵 <br />\n要買飛係常識掛<br />\n咁你無買飛 人地捉你<br />\n好合理姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係你咪唔好搭黨鐵囉<br />\n又要搭 又要唔買飛 <br />\n之後又屌鳩人 <br />\n<br />\n唔知啲人真膠定假膠啦<br />\n成日屌鳩人地check飛<br />\n但其實「買飛搭車」唔洗人提掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:30:09.000Z","msg":"咖啡仔都有得唔執正嚟做啦,佢哋係都要搞死人先安落,你話係咪要屌啊？！"},{"pid":"79dff161cc3ba95b9721bc079591927da5fa4149","tid":2422521,"uid":177873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398ec8191825ff5d463fd60838b4a8347bdbe5f0","tid":2422521,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30787745efc38b912c5eeae5c83e8a85de704230","tid":2422521,"uid":177873,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:27:18.000Z","msg":"其實唔好咁癲啦 <br />\n<br 